# Day 38 – Typing Speed Studio using Claude AI

## Objective
Built an interactive typing practice application to improve typing speed, accuracy, and consistency through multiple typing modes and performance analytics.

## Features
- Multiple Typing Modes
- Live WPM & Accuracy Tracking
- Progress Indicator
- Performance Analytics Dashboard
- Session History
- Theme Switching
- Responsive UI

## Key Learnings
- Designing interactive typing experiences
- Real-time performance calculations
- DOM manipulation with JavaScript
- Building responsive single-page applications
- Creating reusable UI components

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript

## Outcome
Successfully built and tested an offline Typing Speed Studio application with analytics and multiple practice modes.
